{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260421/s00001/d206b344b2cb5b14f8cf98a6e23536b3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>中午12時許，一名男子駕私家車到灣仔軍器廠街警察總部報案，指座駕早前被人損毁。警方經初步調查將案列作刑事毁壞處理。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T06:15:26.398347+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":57,"images":1,"source":"明報 本地","fallback":"none"}}